headline: Keysight Technologies upgraded to Overweight from Neutral at JPMorgan
summary: JPMorgan analyst Samik Chatterjee upgraded Keysight Technologies (KEYS) to Overweight from Neutral with a price target of $200, up from $170. The firm expects a broadening out of the company’s demand drivers along with a cyclical recovery through 2025 in end markets, which have been challenged in 2024.
